quran[47]{c,v,t}:
  26,181,Bixiya beeg dhan oo ha ka mid noqonnina kuwa wax ka dhima
  26,182,Oo wax ku miisaama Miisaan toosan
  26,183,"Oo ha ka dhimina dadka waxyaala- hooda ay xaq u leeyihiin, oo ha ku bi'innina (hallaynina) arlada ku falid fasahaad"
  26,184,Oo iska jira (ciqaabka) Kan idin abuuray idinka iyo uunankii horeba
  26,185,"Waxay yidhaahdeen: Waxaad tahay oo keliya mid ka mid ah kuwa sixran"
  26,186,"Oo ma ahid waxaan ahayn qof nala mid ah, oo waxaanu yaqiinsannahay inaad dhabtii ka mid tahay beenlowyada"
  26,187,Ee nagu soo rid jab samada ah haddii aad ka mid tahay run sheegyada
  26,188,"Wuxuu yidhi: Rabbigay baa Ogsoon waxa aad fashaan"
  26,189,"Wayse beeniyeen, markaasaa cadaab maalintii harka (daruur madow) qabatay, hubaal waxay aheyd cadaab Maalin aad u murugo weyn"
  26,190,"Hubaal, arrinkani waxaa ku sugan xaqiiq calaamo, mase aha badankoodu kuwo rumayn"
  26,191,"Oo hubaal, Rabbigaa waa Isaga Awood Badanaha, Naxariista Badan"
  26,192,"Oo hubaal, kani (Qur’aankani) waa waxyi ka yimid xagga Rabbiga uunanka"
  26,193,Ruuxa aaminka ah (Jabriil) baa la soo degey (oo ku shubay)
  26,194,Qalbigaaga si aad uga mid noqoto Digayaasha
  26,195,Isago af Carabi faseex ah
  26,196,Oo hubaal isla midkani xaqiiq wuxuu ku yaal Kutubtii dadkii hore
  26,197,Miyeyna calaamo u ahayn inay culimidii Banii Israa'iil ay og yihiin
  26,198,Oo haddii aan u soo waxyoon laheyn (Qur’aankani) cajamiga midkood
  26,199,"Oo uu ku dul akhriyi lahaa, ma ay rumeeyeen waxa ku soo arooray"
  26,200,Sidaas baan yeellaa inuu u galo quluubta Dambiilayaasha
  26,201,Ma ay rumayn doonaan jeer ay arkaan cadaabka xanuunka badan
  26,202,"Oo ugu imaan doona si kedis ah, iyagoo aan fileyn"
  26,203,"Markaas bay waxay odhan: Ma nala siinayaa fursad (aan ku rumeyno)"
  26,204,Ee ma cadaabtayada bay degdegsan
  26,205,"Ee ka warran, haddii aan u deyno inay raaxeystaan sanooyin"
  26,206,Markaas uu u yimaado waxaa (ciqaabka) loogu gooddiyo
  26,207,Waxaa loo daayey inay ku raaxeystaan maxay bal u tari doonaan
  26,208,Oo ma jirto magaalo aan halaagno Annagoon marka hore u dirin Digayaal
  26,209,"Si loo waaniyo, oo ma nihin kuwo ku gardarrooda (dadka)"
  26,210,Oo Shaydaammada ma ayan keenin15 (Qur’aankan)
  26,211,"Oo kuma habboona, oo ma leh awood inay isagoo kale keenaan"
  26,212,"Hubaal, waa kuwo xaqiiq laga fogeeyey inay maqalaan isaga"
  26,213,Ee ha la baryin ilaah kale la jirka Allaah yaadan ka mid noqone kuwa la cadaabayo
  26,214,Oo u dig xigtadaada kuu sii dhow
  26,215,Oo u raarici garabkaaga ciddii ku raacda ee ka mid ah mu’miiinta
  26,216,"Haddayse ku caasiyaan markaa dheh: Anigu shaqo kuma lihi waxa aad fashaan"
  26,217,"Oo isku hallee Awood Badanaha, Naxariista Badan"
  26,218,Kan ku arka marka aad kaceyso
  26,219,Iyo gad-gaddoonkaaga dhexdood18 kuwaa u sujuuda (Allaah)
  26,220,"Hubaal, (Allaah) waa wax kasta Maqlaha, wax kasta Ogsoon"
  26,221,Ma idiin sheegaa (dadow) kan ay ku soo degaan shaydaammada
  26,222,"Waxay ku soo degaan beenaale kasta, dambiile ah"
  26,223,"Waxay dhigtaan dhegaha19, oo badankoodu waa beenlawyo"
  26,224,"Oo ma xagga gabyaayada, kuwaa habowsan baa raaca"
  26,225,Miyaadan arag inay dhex wareegaan iyagoo wareersan tog waliba
  26,226,Iyo inay yidhaahdaan waxaysan falayn
  26,227,"Marka laga reebo kuwa (Xaqa) rumeysan oo samaha fala, oo xusa Allaah in badan, oo difaaca nafahooda kaddib marka lagu gardarrooday21. Oo kuwa gefka geysta durba way ogaan doonaan rogmasho noocee ah bay rogmi doonaan"